platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Lots of apps can offer driving directions—but what if you’re not driving at all? That’s where Transit comes in. The travel planning app shows you how to get from point A to point B via train, bus, rideshare—and now even bikeshare and scooter. The app will seek out your best route, offer a few alternate options, and let you know how long you can expect to be in transit.
這款旅行規劃 App 讓你了解如何乘搭火車、巴士、共乘，甚至使用共享單車和滑板車從 A 點到達 B 點。它能為你找到最佳路線，亦能提供替代方案，讓你知道所需時間。

This travel planning app shows you how to get from A to B via train, bus, ride-share – even bike-share and scooter. It will find you the best route, offer a few alternates, and let you know how long it’ll take.
電車、バスなどを使った移動経路を表示してくれるアプリです。おすすめのルートを見つけ、ほかの候補もいくつか提案し、所要時間も教えてくれます。

Whether you’re commuting to work, or hopping a metro in a new city, Transit is your indispensable guide to public transit systems, car- and bike-share services, and more. In addition to live trip-planning updates, Transit will tell you when to leave and give exact step-by-step directions to get you where you need to go.
這款旅遊規劃 App 能幫助你找到最佳路線，提供包括火車、公車、共乘甚至共享單車和滑板車等多種選擇。而且它不僅會為你找到最佳路線，還會提供替代方案，並告訴你所需時間。

Cette app de planification de voyages vous montre comment vous rendre d’un point A à un point B en train, bus ou covoiturage, et même en empruntant un vélo ou en scooter. L’app vous propose le meilleur itinéraire, ainsi que des alternatives et vous indique le temps de trajet.
